data.description: This beautiful custom home is situated on 1.25 sprawling acres with sleek curb appeal! This property is a stunning convergence of contemporary and timeless design - with high-end amenities and modern conveniences, you will feel right at home! From relaxing evenings in front of the fire, game nights in the game/media room to al fresco gatherings, your entertaining options are endless! The foyer is a welcoming introduction and boasts a beautiful set of iron and beveled glass doors. Upscale amenities include detailed ceiling treatments, accent lighting, designer chandeliers reminiscent of art, beautiful hardwood flooring and accented walls.  The great room is truly the heart of this home and features a wall of seamless glass windows, stone fireplace and serene backyard views. Bordering this space is the gourmet kitchen and dining area. The Chef enthusiast will appreciate the culinary haven that is infused with Bosch stainless steel appliances, 6 burner gas range, double ovens, microwave, side-by-side refrigerator/freezer and wine refrigerator,  an abundance of custom cabinetry and workspace, a vast wraparound sitting bar plus a prepping station with a vegetable sink. A wealth of relaxation and serenity, the downstairs primary wing is impressive! Amenities include a spacious bedroom suite with outside access and sitting nook, stepped ceiling treatment and a beautiful accent wall.  Double doors open to the well-designed spa-infused bath that boasts separate floating vanities with accent lighting, beautiful designer flooring, free standing tub and a walk-in shower with dual glass door entries and multiple shower heads. Additional features include ample storage cabinets for towels and toiletries, a separate exercise or flex room and custom wardrobe rooms. Three spacious bedrooms suites, a private study with outside access, mudroom with a seating bench and spacious utility room complete the main level. For relaxed living, the upstairs game/media room is ideal for watching your movies and is the only room situated on the upper level, along with a partial bath. For year-round enjoyment the extensive backyard is ideal for leisure and pets. The expansive covered patio is complete with a striking stone fireplace, open sitting areas and an outdoor kitchen with a Coyote grill, sink and beverage cooler! Vintage Oaks at The Vineyard offers a wide-range of activities for all! There is a resort-style pool, lazy river, children's pool and park, sports courts, fitness center and walking trails! Come experience hill country living at it's finest.
